name: Wakos Circular World. Art prints. Limited Edition
description:
In the world of Wakos, the cycle of life is holistic and infinite, opposite and complimentary, were all gods interact to create and make the earth grow. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 
40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 in on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: Wakos, flying gods. Art Prints. Limited Edition.
description: Wakos are a universe of characters inspired in Peruvian ancient Andean culture and design toys. This print shows the gods of the sky flying through the clouds to foster rain. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 23.4 x 16.5 in on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: Wakos, Dragon. Art print. Limited Edition.
description:
Dragon-SAN. The Andean Dragon is one of the magical creatures in the world of WAKOS. As in other cultures, our dragon is born from the combination of the three sacred animals, the condor (air), the puma (land) and the sneak (underworld). He is a very important and powerful deity. 
Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 in on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: Wakos, Martin Humboldt. Art print. Limited Edition.
description: Wakos are a universe of characters inspired in Peruvian ancient Andean culture and design toys. This print is an example of series which explores the idea of opposition and complementation between elements, a very present concept among Andean philosophy. The character illustrated in this print is Martin Humbolt, a wako who represents true love and monogamy. His name is Martin because he was created as a gift for a friend who wanted to give him to her boyfriend, named Martin, in their two year anniversary. The last name, Humboldt, is given after the name of the species of pinguins found in the Peruvian coasts.  Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 in on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: Wako-San. Art Print. Limited Edition.

name: Big Bertha, retro cannon. Art Print, Limited Edition
description: Yute & Tocuyo by 4D2 Studio are characters inspired in our creative spirit, our capacity to be thinkers and doers and our gregarious nature. "Yute" has big head, full of thoughts. He is the planner, the architect, the engineer of fantastic machines. "Tocuyo" is the test pilot, the mechanic, the adventurer. Both team up to build air, land and water machines that will take them on a journey to figure out who made them and why. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 23.4 x 16.5 in on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: "Phone Home" Limited edition Giclée Art Print
description: Giclée art print from the series Movie Props by 4D2 Studio, our tribute to the art of film. In this case its the movie  "E.T. The Extraterrestrial" by Steven Spielberg, tells a story of the strong relationship between a lovable alien lost in Earth and an American boy named Elliot. This interstellar tale of friendship and sense of belonging is symbolized by the Speak & Spell, a computer toy popular in the 80s which is used as space communicator to contact ET´s family.  The phrase complements the objective of the prop. The Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Alonso Saavedra. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: "E.V.A." Limited edition Giclée Art Print
description: Giclée art print from the series Movie Props by 4D2 Studio, our tribute to the art of film. In this case to the movie  "Wall-E", by Andrew Stanton, tells a story about a charismatic robot living alone in an abandoned, apocalyptic Earth, destroyed by human excessive consumption.  Wall-E´s job is to pile and order the infinite amount of trash left on Earth which he turns into little blocks that eventually turn into skyscrapers of trash. Suddenly his daily, boring and lonely routine is disrupted by a scout robot called E.V.A. with who he falls in love. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Alonso Saavedra. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: "God will be cut". Limited edition Giclée Art Print,
description: Giclée art print from the series Movie Props by 4D2 Studio, our tribute to the art of film. In this case to the movie  "Kill Bill Vol.1", by Quentin Tarantino, tells a story about the power of revenge and will power. The Bride (Uma Thurman) is a ruthless killer who was betrayed by her gang and left for dead. As she surprisingly survived, she decides to pursue and kill those who wrong her one by one. The prop in this print represents The Bride´s unstoppable will and skill to make things right. Even God will not stop her in her mission.  Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist,  Alonso Saavedra. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: "Greed is good". Limited edition Giclée Art Print
description: "Greed is good". Tribute to the movie Wall Street, by Oliver Stone, quote by character Gordon Gekko played by Michael Douglas who won an Oscar for his role. The prop selected is the Motorola "Brick", 80s cellphone. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.

name: "The Dude Abides". Limited edition Giclée Art Print
description: Giclée print from the series Movie Props by 4D2 Studio, a tribute to film, and in this case to the movie  "The Big Lebowsky", by Ethan and Joel Coen. The film is about the odyssey of a lovable L.A. slacker, the "Dude" Lebowsky (Jeff Bridges) who gets involved in a surreal adventure when he tries to get his rug changed because of a misunderstanding. The bowling ball (the prop) represents his "take it easy" attitude towards life, while the phrase "The Dude abides" talks about how he bows, with humility, towards the fate and destiny that unfolds in front of him. The comedy is regard as a cult movie, critical of the fast-pased, success driven US society. Limited Edition Print, signed by the artist, Rafael Lanfranco. 40 prints. Size 16.5 x 11.7 on Innova Fine Art Paper 315 gr 100% cotton. Includes certificate of authenticity.
